column5: I am heading up there in two weeks, and was wondering how the fishing is? Is the water level up? and information would be very much appreciated, feel free to pm me. Thanks again
I am heading up there in two weeks, and was wondering how the fishing is? Is the water level up? and information would be very much appreciated, feel free to pm me. Thanks again

The water level was VERY LOW on June 9th. About a foot and a half to 2 feet, I'd say. Watch out for new rocks. We didn't get out too much on the main lake, stayed mostly to the south end. We were only there for a couple of days, but the fish bit good and the ticks were plentiful.
